terms.medium_def:
A man from the tribe of Benjamin living at the time of Divided Monarchy, only mentioned at 1Ch.8.10; 
only referred to as Mirmah (מִרְמָה); 
son of Shaharaim and Hodesh; 
a brother of Jobab, Zibia, Mesha, Malcam, Jeuz, Sachia, Abitub and Elpaal. § a Benjamite born in the land of Moab
